00:58:09.000 --> 00:58:24.000
So like all the books I write today, they were written with Quarto. I make a free and open source website that everyone can read for free, and then it also creates a PDF that the publisher gets and turns into a physical book.

00:58:24.000 --> 00:58:32.000
