01:20:22.000 --> 01:20:27.000
No, it's just a weird name, but it's, like, it's too late to change it now.

01:20:27.000 --> 01:20:28.000
I like it.

01:20:28.000 --> 01:20:29.000
It makes perfect sense to me.

01:20:29.000 --> 01:20:37.000
Grammar of Graphics Plot 2.

